 ENTER CUSTOMER CODE!                                         06
 CUSTOMER DOES NOT EXIST IN MASTER!                           07
 ENTER DELIVERY CODE!                                         08
 DELIVERY DOES NOT EXIST IN MASTER!                           09
 PRESS F5 TO UPDATE...                                        10
